creator: Natasha Di Marco
descriptionHtml:
Do you prefer REAL FOOD? Do you like to try the real artisan food from different countries? Would you like to share this real food in a catering? APIU app select for you the best Artisan restaurants. You can find exclusive food for you or for your events, also you can program your orders for 2 more days of your week and get this through delivery or pick up options.

GET THE BEST REAL FLAVORS FROM THE SELECTED ARTISAN RESTAURANTS.

Choose the food menu of your preference guaranteeing for you the authentic taste of different cultures.

FIND THE TRUE FLAVOR FOR YOUR CATERING OR EVENT.

Select the date and time of your event, choose artisan food option of your preference and we will prepare it with quality and accuracy. Highlighting our delivery, service or pick up options.

SCHEDULE YOUR MEAL FOR THE WEEK.

We know that you have a busy life. You can program with us your meals per week. you can schedule for 2 or more days of your week and just select the food of your preference the days and the time you need them. We will take care of it to your hands.

PICK UP AND DELIVERY OPTION.

Thinking about its ease, you can choose both options if you want food to be delivered to your hands or if you prefer to pick it up at the store, you can also do it.

ABOUT US.

We are a company destined to provide a traditional food delivery service, always selecting the best that highlight the authentic flavor of different cultures. We also offer Catering and order services for the week.
